ZH: 我平常都在家工作。
EN: I usually work from home.

ZH: 你平常几点起床？
EN: What time do you usually wake up?

ZH: 他平常很少出门。
EN: He rarely goes out.

ZH: 她平常喜欢运动。
EN: She usually likes to exercise.

ZH: 我们平常周末去爬山。
EN: We usually go hiking on weekends.

ZH: 他平常不吃早餐。
EN: He doesn't usually eat breakfast.

ZH: 你平常都做些什么？
EN: What do you usually do?

ZH: 我们平常去健身房锻炼。
EN: We go to the gym to exercise regularly.

ZH: 她平常不喜欢吃辣的食物。
EN: She doesn't usually like to eat spicy food.

ZH: 我们平常都很忙。
EN: We are usually very busy.

ZH: 他平常很注意饮食。
EN: He usually pays a lot of attention to his diet.

ZH: 我平常晚上都会读书。
EN: I usually read books at night.

ZH: 她平常在这个时间段工作。
EN: She usually works during this time.

ZH: 我们平常一起看电影。
EN: We usually watch movies together.

ZH: 他平常都会做运动。
EN: He usually exercises.

ZH: 他平常很少帮助别人。
EN: He rarely helps others.

ZH: 我们平常去那家咖啡店喝咖啡。
EN: We usually go to that coffee shop for coffee.

ZH: 她平常周末会去购物。
EN: She usually goes shopping on weekends.

ZH: 我们平常都会遛狗。
EN: We usually walk the dog.

ZH: 他平常离开家很早。
EN: He usually leaves home very early.
